Countryâ€“Capital Matching Game (React + Vite)

A simple and interactive matching game built using React, Vite, and clean component-based architecture.
The user selects a country and then tries to match it with the correct capital.
Correct pairs highlight in green and disappear; wrong pairs highlight in red and show a temporary message.

Added comments in code for better explanation

ðŸ”§ Installation

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/UP1992/CountryCapitalTask.git
cd country-capital-match


Install dependencies:

npm install


Start development server:

npm run dev
